title: Ubehage's EasyCopy v2.4.1
description:
Ubehage's EasyCopy v2.4.1
-------------------------
"Small, Fast and Easy to use!"

Here is a small update to this user- and nerd-friendly tool for copying/moving around with files and folders.


Fixes in this release:
- Would not show contents of personal folders in File-browser.
